title: Spectral (attribute)

properties.name: description
properties.value: The Spectral attribute is given to monsters who give Prayer XP when killed by players with the Ectoplasmator.

content:
This article is about the monster type. For anything else, see Spectre.

The Spectral attribute is given to monsters who give Prayer XP when killed by players with the Ectoplasmator.

Effects[edit | edit source]

Upon killing a spectral NPC, players with the Ectoplasmator will gain Prayer XP equal to 20% of the monster's max health, rounded down.
